# Backend Conventions — EVNICT Standard
> QĐ-TTPM Điều 8, Mục 8.6 | Java Spring Boot + JOOQ + Oracle

## RB01: Input Validation
- @Valid + @NotNull, @NotBlank, @Size, @Pattern trên DTO
- Whitelist sort columns: `ALLOWED_SORT.contains(sortBy)`

## RB02: Service Layer Pattern
- Controller: validate input, call service, return ResponseData
- Service: business logic, @Transactional
- Repository: data access ONLY (JOOQ)
- DTO: data transfer — KHÔNG dùng Entity cho response

## RB03: Error Handling
```java
@RestControllerAdvice
GlobalExceptionHandler {
  BusinessException → ResponseData.error(msg)
  ValidationException → ResponseData.error(field errors)
  Exception → log.error(full), return "Có lỗi xảy ra" (NO stack trace)
}
```

## RB04: Database Migration
- Flyway: `V{YYYYMMDD}_{seq}__{desc}.sql` + rollback
- KHÔNG raw DDL trong Java code

## RB05: Auth Every Route
- Default deny: `.anyRequest().authenticated()`
- Public → whitelist rõ ràng: `/api/auth/login`, `/actuator/health`
- @PreAuthorize cho role/data-level auth

## RB06: Rate Limiting
- API public (login) → rate limit BẮT BUỘC

## JOOQ Conventions
- `fetchInto(DTO.class)` thay vì manual mapping
- Pagination: `.offset(page * size).limit(size)`
- @Transactional ở Service layer

## Naming
- Class: PascalCase (`CustomerService`), Method: camelCase
- Table/Column: UPPER_SNAKE (`CUSTOMER`, `CREATED_DATE`)
- File: `{Module}Controller.java`, `{Module}Service.java`, `{Module}DTO.java`
